channel.title: An API for Moparscape?
channel.description:
Is there one?
I looked in the moparscape folder and did not find any documentation. If I am missing it, please tell me where it is? I mainly need this to understand everything I can do. I could just as well go up to everything in Eclipse and put a dot after it to see what methods it has, but I would much rather like some docs. I am new here so if I missed them, just point me in the right direction please. I already did a forum search for them, which returned nothing.
Oh, also, it's nice to be part of the group now! I look forward to programming this client.
